《'''联合航空砸烂了我的吉他'''》（United Breaks Guitars，也译作“联航损坏了吉他”）是一首抗議歌曲，由[[戴夫·卡羅爾|戴夫·卡羅爾]]（Dave Carroll）及其樂隊[[馬克斯韋爾之子|馬克斯韋爾之子]]（Sons of Maxwell）所創作。歌曲內容是他本人在2008年搭乘[[聯合航空|聯合航空]]時，聯航損壞他的[[吉他|吉他]]及公司對待他的真實經歷。2009年7月，歌曲發佈在[[YouTube|YouTube]]和[[iTunes|iTunes]]後立即爆紅，同時使聯航面臨一場[[公關災難|公關災難]]。

==事源 ==
2008年，戴夫·卡羅爾乘搭聯合航空從[[加拿大|加拿大]][[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]][[哈利法克斯勞勃·羅恩·史坦菲國際機場|勞勃·羅恩·史坦菲國際機場]]（Halifax Stanfield International Airport）出發前往美國[[内布拉斯加州|内布拉斯加州]][[奥马哈_(内布拉斯加州)|奧馬哈]][[艾波萊機場|艾波萊機場]]（Eppley Airfield），中停[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[歐海爾國際機場|歐海爾國際機場]]（O'Hare International Airport）時，他把他的吉他托運。卡羅爾稱他聽到部份乘客目睹机场的行李托運員拋擲他的吉他。落地後他發現價值3,500美元的泰勒吉他已嚴重損壞<ref name="CNN"/>。[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]質問為何把如此貴重的吉他托運，他回應指難以把吉他作為手提行李帶上飛機<ref name="Fox News">{{Cite episode| title = Fox News| url = http://video.foxnews.com/v/3935170/united-breaks-guitars| series = Fox & Friends| network = Fox News Channel| airdate = July 9, 2009| access-date = 2013-10-24| archive-date = 2021-03-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210307212406/https://video.foxnews.com/v/3935170/united-breaks-guitars| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在歌中他提及他向三名聯航員工反映，但他們對此事顯得漠不關心。卡羅爾嘗試向聯航追討賠償，但聯航以「超過24小時」為由拒絕<ref name=cosh20090821>{{cite news |url=http://www.financialpost.com/scripts/story.html?id=f9065720-c55a-4612-84eb-e168fd37ed1f&k=15437 |title=A man and his guitar |first=Colby |last=Cosh |work=National Post |location=Canada |date=August 21, 2009 |publisher=The Financial Post |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305172232/http://www.financialpost.com/scripts/story.html?id=f9065720-c55a-4612-84eb-e168fd37ed1f&k=15437 |archivedate=2012年3月5日 }}</ref>。事後他花了1,200美元自行維修吉他,但吉他的音色差了。

==歌曲==
卡羅爾指他事後被聯航要求填寫各式各樣的表格，與聯航展開長達9個月的追討戰，但徒勞無功<ref name=cbc/>。後來想起美國知名紀錄片導演[[麥可·摩爾|麥可·摩爾]]（Micheal Moore）的經歷，於是以他的經歷創作了一首歌曲<ref name=tel20090723/>，由他本人主唱，歌詞提到「我本应该搭乘其他航空公司航班或者開車去，因聯航會損壞我的吉他」（I should have flown with someone else, or gone by car, 'cause United breaks guitars.）<ref name=upi>[http://www.upi.com/Odd_News/2009/07/09/Singers-revenge-on-United-A-hit-song/UPI-79301247160917/ ''Singer's revenge on United: A hit song''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.upi.com/Odd_News/2009/07/09/Singers-revenge-on-United-A-hit-song/UPI-79301247160917/ |date=20151118154055 }} United Press International July 9, 2009.</ref>。此歌亦有續集<ref name="guar20090723"/>，於2009年8月17日上傳<ref>{{YouTube|id=h-UoERHaSQg|title="United Breaks Guitars Song 2"}}</ref>，歌曲諷刺聯航員工須擁護這有瑕疵的制度。第3集在2010年3月上傳<ref name="davecarrollmusic1">{{cite web |url=http://www.davecarrollmusic.com/2010/02/lead-story-one/ |title=United Breaks Guitars: Song 3 – Dave Carroll |publisher=Davecarrollmusic.com |date=February 17, 2010 |accessdate=April 30, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820122538/http://www.davecarrollmusic.com/2010/02/lead-story-one/ |archivedate=2010年8月20日 }}</ref>，歌中指不是所有聯航員工都是壞蘋果，最後一句說「你說你們改善中，我希望是真的，不然誰會搭你們的飛機」（They say that you're [United] changing and I hope you do, 'Cause if you don't then who would fly with you?）<ref name="davecarrollmusic1"/>。

==迴響==
影片於2009年7月6日上傳，即日便吸引超過150,000人次觀看，使聯航不得不與卡羅爾接觸修補錯誤<ref name=cbc>[http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/story/2009/07/08/united-breaks-guitars.html Broken guitar song gets airline's attention] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/story/2009/07/08/united-breaks-guitars.html |date=20100507023207 }} ''CBC News. Online'', July 8, 2009. Retrieved July 8, 2009.</ref>。3天後瀏覽人次已超過100萬，至2018年4月有超過1,800萬人次觀看。

傳媒報導了此歌曲的迅速爆紅，及聯航即將面對的公關災難<ref name="CNN">{{cite episode|first=Wolf|last=Blitzer|authorlink=|date=9 July 2009|title=United Breaks Guitars|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QDkR-Z-69Y|accessdate=2 March 2013|network=CNN|series=The Situation Room|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316101107/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QDkR-Z-69Y|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=tel20090723>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/travelnews/5892082/Musician-behind-anti-airline-hit-video-United-Breaks-Guitars-pledges-more-songs.html |title=Musician behind anti-airline hit video 'United Breaks Guitars' pledges more songs |first=Alastair |last=Jamieson |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=July 23, 2009 |location=London |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308160934/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/travelnews/5892082/Musician-behind-anti-airline-hit-video-United-Breaks-Guitars-pledges-more-songs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=guar20090723>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/blog/2009/jul/23/youtube-united-breaks-guitars-video |title=Singer gets his revenge on United Airlines and soars to fame |work=The Guardian |date=July 23, 2009 |location=London |first=Mark |last=Tran |accessdate=May 26, 2010 |archive-date=2011-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111224025218/http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/blog/2009/jul/23/youtube-united-breaks-guitars-video |dead-url=no }}</ref>。聯航發言人為了製造對聯航有正面影響的假象，指此歌「十分棒」。聯航公關總監親自致電給卡羅爾道歉，並且會用此歌曲加強對員工的培訓，汲取教訓<ref name=cbc/>。

[[泰勒吉他|泰勒吉他]]創辦人立刻致電給卡羅爾，提供兩個吉他和其它道具協助拍攝第二部短片<ref name=guar20090723/>。影片上傳一星期後立即登上iTunes每週音樂之最首位<ref name=star20091029>{{cite news |url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/article/717968--united-loses-luggage-of-united-breaks-guitars-guy |title=United loses luggage of 'United Breaks Guitars' guy |first=Jesse |last=McLean |work=Toronto Star |date=October 29, 2009 |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2013-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102055240/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/article/717968--united-loses-luggage-of-united-breaks-guitars-guy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然聯航賠償了3,000美元，但無助修補此歌曲帶來的負面形象<ref name=times20090722>{{cite news |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/law/columnists/article2051377.ece |title=Revenge is best served cold – on YouTube |first=Chris |last=Ayers |work=The Times |date=July 22, 2009 |location=London |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2015-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914015251/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/law/columnists/article2051377.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

之後卡羅爾又一次搭乘聯合航空，但聯航遺失了他的行李<ref name=star20091029/>。

2009年12月，[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]把此歌評選為2009年十大病毒歌曲中的第7位<ref name="timevv">{{cite news |first=Dan |last=Fletcher |work=TIME |title=Top 10 Viral Videos – 7. United Breaks Guitars |url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1945379_1945171_1945170,00.html |date=December 8, 2009 |quote=Fuming about mishandled baggage? Singing's the best revenge. |accessdate=2013-10-24 |archive-date=2013-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826180651/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1945379_1945171_1945170,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

